# Enterprise (enterprise flat ride): the rotating wheel with rigidly-
# attached pods. Disc in the X-Y plane, axle along Z, centred at the origin
# (the spin lifts it to the hub). The truss supports are base-game
# graphics, so the object provides only the wheel; the pods rotate WITH the
# wheel (riders invert), unlike the ferris wheel's upright gondolas.
# OBJ space: +X forward, +Y up, +Z right; origin at footprint-base centre.
mtllib materials.mtl

